overview: Ignacio Aranguren Castiell serves as an Executive Chairman and Chief Executive Officer at Arancia Industrial S.A. de CV. Mr. Castiell serves as an Executive Director of at Arancia Industrial S.A. de CV. Mr. Castiell has worked in finance, strategy, corn supply, and plant management for oils and urfactants. Mr. Castiell served at Hewlett-Packard. Mr. Castiell is an Electrical Engineer from the University of Notre Dame. Mr. Castiell obtained an M.B.A. from Stanford. .
